Text: HCS IzioPro SurveyHaas Students Haas Computing Services would like to thank you for participating in the IzioPro Learning Management System pilot for the fall semester HCS is conducting a survey as part of the evaluation of the Learning Management System The link below will take you to the survey There will be a authentication screen that opens when you click on the link The name and password required to login is your Haas domain login Thank you in advance for your participation HCSiziosurvey As always Haas Computing Services is pleased to assist you with any support issues if you contact the Help Desk at mailto or William Starks Assistant Director FacultyPhD Computing Haas School of Business University of California Berkeley Office Phone mailto
